Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan bertarung demi kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kekuatanku sendiri\Ntidak bisa melindungi kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pinjamkan kekuatan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari lindungi desa ini bersama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kami siap bertempur!\N- Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo lindungi sama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, naik ke benteng!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ayo!\N- Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelompok Ortho sedang berburu,\Ntidak ada di desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku yang urus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Till?\NAku juga harus pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dee, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naiklah dan laporkan situasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan beri instruksi dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dee, berapa jumlah Kadal Zirahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekitar 40 ekor kelas 8 meter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu ekor saja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sulit dibasmi walau dikeroyok\Nkesatria veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dee! Muat panah besi ke balista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Dee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kulit keras mereka kebal senjata biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski ikut pertarungan yang mustahil,\Naku selalu berhasil menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang pun, aku ingin coba\Nmengikuti instruksi Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muat panah besi ke balista!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersiap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panahnya lenyap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepuluh Kadal Zirah berhasil tumbang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat sekali balista Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tiap balista cuma sisa satu panah besi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini, tembok kita bisa jebol!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus menembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya! Isi ulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gelombang kedua tumbang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi panah besinya habis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Dee, desa bisa hancur!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dee, gunakan panah kayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panah kayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau kayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisik Kadal Zirah itu sekeras baja!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini,\NTuan Van selalu melampaui dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melindungi desa dari bandit\Ndan memajukannya dengan pesat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memercayai Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isi panah kayu dan bersiap tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepala mereka tertembus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Dee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serang! Malam ini kita pesta sate kadal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua Kadal Zirah mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Musuh kalah telak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita nol korban jiwa,\Nbahkan tidak ada yang terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panah yang terpakai pun cuma sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemenangan besar,\Nbahkan terasa terlalu mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van pasti jadi orang besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melebihi bayangan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Simpan mata dan taringnya baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buang jeroannya, tapi ambil inti sihirnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlah sebanyak ini
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seharusnya busuk sebelum kelar dipotong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat pisau buatan Tuan Van,\Nkerja jadi lancar jaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, dagingnya banyak sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, hari ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita adakan pesta besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari rayakan kemenangan ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama tidak minum sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, panggang dagingnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka ada hari
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita bisa makan enak\Nsambil tertawa bersama lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih ada bangsawan yang mau\Ntertawa bersama kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski sebagai bangsawan,\Nsikap ini kurang pantas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah pesona Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luarnya renyah, dalamnya lembut berair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daging Kadal Zirah ini enak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal panah balista,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ternyata bahannya sama seperti\Nyang dibuat untuk senjata kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van membuatkan pedang\Nuntuk kelompok Ortho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa memotong tulang monster tanpa hambatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ramping, ringan, dan mudah dipakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuk dan ketajamannya mantap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van!\NAku juga mau beli!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa harga pedang besar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau satu set pedang panjang dan belati!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa terima uang dari kalian\Nyang sudah berjasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bahan dan kas desa stabil,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}nanti kuberi satu set lengkap, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Kadal Zirah kita jual ke pedagang,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin laku 20 koin emas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebanyak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, karena dagingnya cepat busuk\Ndan tidak bisa dijual,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu dipotong biaya transportasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}satu ekor cuma seharga 8 koin emas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi karena ada 40 ekor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa dapat 300 koin emas lebih, dong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dikonversi ke yen Jepang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}300 juta yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau desa memperoleh\Nlebih dari 100 koin emas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada aturan wajib setor setengahnya\Nke keluarga Marquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa dirahasiakan saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlah sebanyak ini pasti ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira bisa dapat 300 juta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata cuma 150 juta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan masalahnya adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah bakal tahu kondisi desa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dia tahu desa ini menguntungkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bakal dilempar ke tempat lain
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tidak bisa hidup santai lagi di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit merahasiakannya, tapi ada solusi lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita laporkan ini pada kakak Tuan Van,\NTuan Murcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke kakakku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Jadi seolah-olah Kakak\Nyang membasmi Kadal Zirah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, kakak juga butuh pencapaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesepakatan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van, ada pedagang keliling\Nmenuju kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, benarkah ini desa terpencil itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tidak salah jalan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian pasti pedagang keliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penguasa desa ini, Van Nei Fertio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia putra keempat Marquis Fertio, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si "Anak Ajaib" jadi penguasa di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa beri tahu nama\Ndan perusahaan dagang kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Bell dari Perusahaan Dagang Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan dia Rango, adikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di desa kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Material Kadal Zirah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian membasmi Kadal Zirah sebanyak ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makhluk yang ditakuti petualang\Ndibasmi desa kecil begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian mau beli?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kami harus cari pekerja dulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa tunggu sebulan\Nsampai pengiriman diproses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dagingnya tidak tahan lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}silakan ambil secara gratis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai gantinya,\Nkami punya senjata berkualitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di desa ini ada pandai besi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kami beli sesuai harga tawaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, bisa promosikan senjata kami juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pasti ingin menjualnya\Nsecara eksklusif.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian naif sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kalian menjual senjata yang sama\Nlewat rute yang sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang bakal tahu senjata itu\Nbuatan desa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya promosikan saja sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin banyak terjual, makin besar untungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bagaimana caranya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buka toko di desa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toko kami sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa bisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah diputuskan,\Nayo langsung bangun tokonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hah?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal baru saja menyampaikan\Nkonsep tokonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit dipercaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, mohon kerja samanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kulihat sendiri sosok "Anak Ajaib" itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membangun kota untuk sepuluh ribu jiwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat perkembangan ke depan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik bangun benteng skala\Nsepuluh ribu orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini, seribu saja tidak cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat laju perkembangan desa,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sepuluh ribu pun masih kurang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau terus berkembang,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita perlu banyak SDM untuk mengelola fasilitas
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjaga keamanan desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah kalau menurutmu begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti apa benteng yang Tuan inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, benteng persegi paling umum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sebenarnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin benteng bentuk bintang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyerang akan makan waktu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menaklukkan sudut sebelum sampai pusat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau nekat menjebol tembok,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka akan diserang dari tiga arah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuk yang dipikirkan dengan matang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van, gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada utusan dari tetangga kita,\NCount Ferdinatto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utusan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam, aku Van Nei Fertio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dipercaya sebagai penguasa desa ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Panamera Karla Kaien.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru-baru ini diangkat jadi Viscount.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naik status dari gelar kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku putri bungsu Count Ferdinatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Arut Ann Ferdinatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah mengutusku untuk memberi salam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sa-Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga, salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah bersedia datang\Nke desa yang kekurangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan duduk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tampaknya lebih muda dari Putri Arut,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu terlihat cukup tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut Tuan Van, kenapa kami ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengamati dan pendekatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Usia delapan tahun, tapi berpikir sejauh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dugaanmu tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Count Ferdinatto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat waspada karena perbatasan\Nwilayah Count dan Yelenetta ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dipegang oleh Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beliau khawatir kamulah ujung tombak\Nambisi Marquis Fertio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengingat "anak ajaib" malah dibuang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kemungkinan besar kamu bukan\Npengguna empat elemen sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Disembunyikan pun bakal ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Bukan pengguna empat elemen sihir"\Nmemang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kekhawatiran lainnya berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma orang yang diusir ayah sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebohongan yang terlalu jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Desa berpenduduk seratus orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dalam waktu singkat membangun tembok kokoh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memperbarui semua bangunan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya butuh lima ribu pekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu demi menjadikan\Ndesa ini basis militer baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NTidak bisa membantah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apanya yang lucu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu terlalu serius, jadi lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tertawa terlalu keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan kuluruskan kesalahpahaman ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesalahpahaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah cuma mengizinkanku
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membawa Kamshin yang di situ\Ndan satu kereta barang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa diantar keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, bagaimana dengan pelayan\Ndan kesatria itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melihat masa depan pada\Nbakat pedang dan potensi Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ikut sukarela.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan aku mengabaikan surat perintah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau diabaikan, kamu bisa dipecat, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai yang kamu lihat, aku sudah tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat dengar Tuan Van ke pedesaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kupikir ini kesempatan pensiun dan ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai hobi masa tua,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin ajarkan seluruh ilmuku\Npada Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hobi yang merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski Tuan Van bangsawan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia memperlakukan kalangan bawah\Nseperti kami dengan setara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat memikirkan orang lain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sifat baiknya membuatku ingin mengabdi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, begitulah situasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}La-Lalu bagaimana dengan\Nperubahan drastis desa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kutunjukkan langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya area ini cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku akan buat tembok benteng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kamu pengguna Empat Elemen kelas satu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau cuma begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat mana habis, tembok akan runtuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sip, beginilah hasilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf, sebenarnya apa atribut sihirmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Produksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Umumnya, disebut sihir paling tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat tahu atributku tipe produksi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku langsung diusir,\Njadi ayah tidak tahu kekuatanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.\NSayang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dengan kekuatanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keluarga Marquis bisa memperluas kekuasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit dipercaya, tapi aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diperintah mendorong pertunangan\NTuan Van dan Putri Arut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi itu alasan Putri Arut datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengirim putri untuk mencegah konflik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih berencana memperkuat tembok
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membangun desa lebih besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tidak ada niat untuk berkonflik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin kalian tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tidak perlu menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku menentang pertunangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasangannya anak kecil\Npenguasa desa terpencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah dia kompeten atau tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Arut mungkin tidak akan bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diperlakukan dingin,\Nhidup di pelosok tanpa uang,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau mati diserang bandit dan monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku ikut untuk mencegahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku berubah pikiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tunangannya Tuan Van,\Naku sangat setuju,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemikiran yang tidak seperti anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemampuan menyatukan rakyat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mental dan pengetahuan mengatasi kesulitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serta kekuatan sihir luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kita seumuran,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pasti mengajukan diri jadi tunanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dipuji! Senang banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya tinggal kesediaan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, Putri Arut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku tidak ada yang lebih baik darinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku, eng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku Tuan Van orang yang baik,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku belum mengenalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga belum kepikiran menikah, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang jelas, ini harus dipikirkan baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kita menginap,\Npikirkanlah matang-matang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Mau menginap?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku bisa lihat sisi asli Tuan Van.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari tadi sikapnya tidak seperti anak-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Arut bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau menginap,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidur di kediaman Tuan Van juga boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ti-tidur di kamar laki-laki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudah, Putri Arut tidur sekamar denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Van, ada kamar yang bisa digunakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kubangun penginapan sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibangun secepat ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Arut, enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai bahannya ada,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa buatkan manisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak, ini sudah enak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada hal yang Putri Arut sukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku suka hal-hal yang lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, tuh, hal-hal lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang seperti apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Seperti bunga atau boneka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jarang melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau boleh,\Nlain kali bisa tunjukkan padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Bo-Boleh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bonekanya tertinggal di kereta,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi mungkin besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, apa aku juga boleh lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah waktunya tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Te-Terima kasih banyak untuk hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gugup karena perjodohan ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ta-tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat Tuan Van sangat baik, aku jadi lega.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Selamat malam!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, mungkin penilaiannya\Ntidak terlalu buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena Putri Arut dikirim untuk bertunangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia juga bukan pengguna\NSihir Empat Elemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti sulit mengatakan\Nkalau dia diusir sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang terpenting keinginan Putri Arut.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau memang tidak bisa pulang,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia bisa tinggal di sini tanpa menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ingin pulang, kita turuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Sudah menyatakan cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Arut, rencananya besok kita pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa mau tinggal beberapa hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.33,0:23:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau besok bertemu Tuan Van,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mau menyapa duluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah lama tidak sesemangat ini\Nmenunggu esok.
